      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LITTLE DULCIE (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (17.18) at this track behind Needle And Seat in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can find winning form. JACKPOT JACK (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Latest effort finished 6th over 300m at this track beaten 5 lengths (17.48) behind Bugatti Step in a Grade 4/5 on March 26. Can hit the frame with the right run. REALITY ZERO (3) has been out of the placings at his last couple of runs but impressed when posting a powerful 16.74 over 300m at this track three starts back. Top win three back and rates a key player again. MR. MORNINGSTAR (8) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
